---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Brick & Mortar Retail Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/ecommerce-retail/brick-and-mortar" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Brick & Mortar Retail
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Retail</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">12 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Brick & Mortar Retail Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Build your customer database, drive foot traffic, and turn one-time shoppers into regulars.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Physical retail isn't dead—it's evolving. The stores that thrive are those that combine in-person experience with digital marketing.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Building Your Customer Database</h2>

          <p>
            Most retail stores let customers walk out anonymously. That's a massive missed opportunity. Every customer could be a repeat customer—if you can reach them.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">Capture Methods That Work</h3>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl my-6">
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-0">
              <li><strong>Loyalty program sign-up:</strong> Instant 10% discount for joining</li>
              <li><strong>QR codes at checkout:</strong> "Text SAVE to 12345 for today's deal"</li>
              <li><strong>WiFi capture:</strong> Free WiFi requires email</li>
              <li><strong>Contest entry:</strong> Monthly giveaway for email/SMS subscribers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Driving Foot Traffic</h2>

          <p>
            Once you have a database, you can drive traffic when you need it most. Slow Tuesday? Send a flash sale. New inventory? Alert your VIPs first.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Competing with Online</h2>

          <p>
            You can't beat Amazon on price or convenience. But you can offer experience, community, and instant gratification that online can't match.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your Store?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd build your customer database and drive foot traffic.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
